  <brief_title>Total Laparoscopic Hysterectomy vs Minilap Hysterectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized Study Comparing Total Laparoscopic Hysterectomy (Lap Hysterectomy) vs Minilaparotomy (Mini-lap Hysterectomy) for Benign Uterine Lesions: Peri-operative Outcome</official_title>
